other.consume: Throws the Snax, which the  Poro King catches in his mouth. Eating the Espresso Snax causes the Poro King to  leap toward a nearby location, aiming to hit as many enemies as possible. After a brief delay, he then leaps back to his original location. Enemies hit take 40 − 190 (based on level) physical damage and are  knocked aside. He also gains a decaying shield for 20% of his maximum health, lasting 4 seconds. (30 seconds cooldown)
other.limit: Can only be used within 850 units of the  Poro King.
